@Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5135

# ========================================
# API Information
# ========================================
# Rate Limiting: 100 requests per minute per IP
# Response: 429 Too Many Requests if exceeded
# Swagger UI: http://localhost:5135/swagger

### Health Check
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

# ========================================
# Category Endpoints
# ========================================

### Get All Categories
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/category
Accept: application/json

### Search Categories with Filters
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/category?text=work&pageSize=20&offset=0
Accept: application/json

### Get Category by ID
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/category/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Accept: application/json

### Create Category
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/category
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Work Projects"
}

### Update Category
PUT {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/category/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Work"
}

### Delete Category
DELETE {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/category/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

###

# ========================================
# List Endpoints
# ========================================

### Get All Lists
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/list
Accept: application/json

### Search Lists with Filters
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/list?text=shopping&includeArchived=false&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

### Get List by ID
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/list/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Accept: application/json

### Create List
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/list
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Grocery Shopping",
  "categoryId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001"
}

### Update List (Rename)
PUT {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/list/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Weekly Grocery Shopping"
}

### Close/Archive List
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/list/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/close

### Open/Unarchive List
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/list/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/open

### Delete List
DELETE {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/list/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

###

# ========================================
# List Item Endpoints
# ========================================

### Get All Items in a List
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/lists/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/items
Accept: application/json

### Search List Items with Filters
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/lists/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/items?text=milk&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

### Create List Item
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/lists/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Buy milk",
  "dueDate": "2026-05-15T10:00:00Z"
}

### Create List Item without Due Date
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/lists/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Buy bread",
  "dueDate": null
}

### Get List Item by ID
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/lists/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/items/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002
Accept: application/json

### Rename List Item
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/lists/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/items/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002/rename
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Buy organic milk"
}

### Set List Item Due Date
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/lists/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/items/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002/due-date
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dueDate": "2026-05-16T10:00:00Z"
}

### Clear List Item Due Date
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/lists/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/items/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002/due-date
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dueDate": null
}

### Reorder List Item (Set Sort Index)
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/lists/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/items/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sortIndex": 5
}

### Toggle List Item Completion
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/lists/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/items/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002/toggle

### Delete List Item
DELETE {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/lists/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/items/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002

###

# ========================================
# Global List Item Search
# ========================================

### Search All List Items Across All Lists
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/listitems?text=urgent&pageSize=50&offset=0
Accept: application/json

###

